@node not2 "FREE UPGRADE TO TORNADO3D V1.75 IS AVAILABLE"

@{FG Shine}FREE UPGRADE TO @{B}TORNADO3D V1.75@{UB} IS AVAILABLE@{FG Text}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
@{FG Fill}DATE: 1998/06/08@{FG Text}

@{I}FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE @{UI}

The "FREE @{B}2.0@{UB}" special offer has been extended to June, the 30th 1998.

May  3rd,  1998  - @{B}Version 1.75@{UB} of @{B}Tornado3D@{UB}, the most advanced 3D rendering and
animation  software for @{B}Amiga@{UB} and @{B}DraCo@{UB} computers, adds @{B}PowerPC@{UB} support and many
other hi-end features.

@{I}What's new? @{UI}

   o @{B}PowerPC@{UB} final and interactive rendering - 6 to 9 times faster than @{B}060@{UB}!
   o MetaQuadric   Surfaces  for  organic  implicit  modeling  -  with  a  fast,
     proprietary, algorithm.
   o Much Faster implicit modeling - interactive performance at detail level 50!
   o Much Improved Metameshing - now with Edge Tension for mechanical modeling.
   o Automatic Normals Alignment - no more flipping!
   o Adaptive Fractal Triangles - a 10x10 mesh becomes as detailed as a
     10000x10000 one.
   o Fractal  Brownian  landscapes  generator  - not the usual "same-everywhere"
     fractals.

Plus:  Timecode  Fast  Jump,  New  Animation  Panel  with  dragging and scaling,
Adaptive  @{B}"Postscript  Type  1"@{UB}  Font  Import,  Font  Beveling, Extended Project
Format,  Improved  Transparent  Rendering,  Path  To  Keyframe, Clouds and Crust
Texture, Terrain Texture and many more bug-fixes and improvements.

Registered  users can receive the @{B}1.75@{UB} update for free, from @{B}Tornado3D@{UB}'s totally
revamped WWW site:
                            @{B}http://www.tornado3d.com@{UB}

The package's serial number is required to fill the update form.

@{I}About @{B}Tornado3D @{UB}@{UI}

@{B}Tornado3D@{UB}  is  a  powerful, integrated, 3D graphics package oriented towards the
professional  market.  @{B}Tornado3D@{UB}  brings  to  the  @{B}Amiga@{UB} the latest in hi-end 3D
graphics  technology,  yet  it  is popularly priced. And as a "thank you" to its
ever  expanding  @{B}Amiga@{UB}  and  @{B}DraCo@{UB}  user base, @{B}Eyelight@{UB} is pleased to extend the
"FREE @{B}V2.0@{UB}" special offer until June the 30th, 1998.

@{I}About @{B}Eyelight @{UB}@{UI}

@{B}Eyelight@{UB}  is  a  dynamic firm, specializing in computer animation and multimedia
production,  located  in  the  charming capital of Italy, Rome, in close contact
with some of Europe's largest cinema and video production facilites.

