@node not26 "NEWS FROM SOFTLOGIK"

@{FG Shine}NEWS FROM @{B}SOFTLOGIK@{UB}@{FG Text}
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
@{FG Fill}DATE: 1998/06/30@{FG Text}

The following is from @{B}SoftLogik@{UB}'s web site.

@{B}SoftLogik@{UB}  has  several  projects  in the works for the @{B}Amiga@{UB}. We'd thought we'd
outline  our  upcoming plans, while some dates on these projects are sketchy, we
wanted  you  to  know  we are still committed to supporting the @{B}Amiga@{UB} for a long
time to come.

@{B}PageStream 3.3b@{UB}

This  release  will  be  the  last  update to @{B}PageStream 3.3@{UB}/@{B}3.2@{UB}/@{B}3.1 Amiga@{UB}. This
version fixes a couple obscure but difficult to fix bugs, and adds a couple much
needed  features.  Beta  testing will be limited to @{B}3.3@{UB} owners initially and the
beta  versions will be posted in the @{B}PageStream 3@{UB} secure ftp site. Betas will be
made available as we go. Initial beta will be up Friday, May 7th.

     @{I}Potential @{B}3.3b @{UB}features: @{UI}
      o Edit text hooks for extensions.
      o Revamp styletags, including: Styletag delete loop.
      o Character/Paragraph combo.
      o Styletag override.
      o Undo/Redo: Fix in/out of page/spread/pasteboard undo remainder of object
        editing.
      o Dynamically move articles to proper document/chapter level.
      o Spell Checking.
      o Color palette for text.
      o Reshape path curves->lines->curves and closing.
      o Min/Max/Opt Word/Character spacing.

@{B}PageStream 3.4@{UB}

@{B}PageStream  3.4@{UB}  will  be  a very minor cost upgrade to @{B}Amiga@{UB} owners. The actual
