@{B}F1  Software@{UB}  have  just  signed  up a brand new shareware music creator for the
@{B}Amiga@{UB}  called  @{B}BEATBOX  2@{UB}  (@{B}http://www.ware5d.demon.co.uk/beatbox.htm@{UB}).  You can
download  the  very  latest version now from the @{B}F1@{UB} website at the address shown
above. Surf across now and give it a whirl.

