from  America. To get your hands on the registration keyfile costs just 7.00GBP,
details are included in the archive.

Music  doesn't get any easier! Ok, what is it then? It's a music editing system,
but with a difference. Instead of wading through a bunch of hex numbers, you can
enter your song with an easy to use point and click graphic interface.

Features include:

  1. Works on ANY @{B}Amiga@{UB} with @{B}WB 2.01@{UB} or better.
  2. GFX card compatable.
  3. Many user options.
  4. Use any @{I}.iff @{UI}sound samples (up to 99 per song).
  5. Online help (through @{B}MultiView@{UB}).
  6. Online program prefs, including screenmode and font selection.
  7. Easy and fun to use (no musical knowledge necessary).
  8. Now with supersonic load/save routines.
  9. Example song included.

